3-ne 12:
[center][font_size=26]Upoko 12[/font_size][/center]

[i]Ka karangatia, ā, ka whakamanaia ngā apataki tekau mā rua e Ihu—Ka tukuna atu tētahi kauhau e ia ki ngā Nīwhai e rite ana ki te Kauhautanga i runga i te Maunga—Ka kōrero ia i ngā Pearature—Kei kō noa atu āna whakaakoranga, ā, he nui ake te hiranga o āna whakaakoranga i tō te ture a Mohi—Ka whakahaua te tangata kia tino tika rawa atu pērā i a rāua ko Tōna Matua tika—Whakatauritetia a Matiu 5. Takiwā T.A. 34.[/i]

1 Ā, i pahawa ake, nā, i te kōrerotanga a Ihu i ēnei kupu ki a Nīwhai, ki te hunga anō hoki kua karangatia ake nei, (ko te tatauranga o te hunga i karangatia nei, ā, i whakawhiwhi ai ki te kaha me te mana ki te rumaki, arā, ko te tekau mā rua) ā nana, ka toro atu ia i tōna ringa ki te whakaminenga, ā, ka karanga atu ki a rātou, e mea ana: Ka manaakitia koutou mēnā ka whakarongo mai ki ngā kupu a te tekau mā rua kua kōwhiria ake nei i waenganui i a koutou kia minita ai ki a koutou, ā, kia mahi anō hei pononga mā koutou; ā, kua tukuna atu e au he kaha e rumaki ai rātou i a koutou ki te wai; ā, hei muri iho i tā koutou rumakitanga ki te wai, nana, māku koutou e rumaki ki te ahi me te Wairua Tapu; nō reira ka manaakitia koutou mēnā ka whakapono koutou i ahau, ā, mēnā ka rumakitia, whai muri iho i tā koutou kitenga i ahau, ā, e mōhio ana ko au anō tēnei.

2 Hei āpiti anō, ka manaakitia ake te hunga e whakapono ai ki ā koutou kupu nā te mea ka whakaatu atu koutou i tā koutou kitenga mai i ahau, ā, e mōhio ana koutou ko au anō tēnei. Āe rā, ka manaakitia te hunga e whakapono ai ki ā koutou kupu, me te heke iho ki roto i ngā hōhonutanga o te whakaiti, ā, kia rumakina ai, nā te mea ka torona atu koutou ki te ahi me te Wairua Tapu, ā, ka whiwhi ki tētahi murunga i ō rātou hara.

3 Āe rā, ka manaakitia te hunga e rawakore ana i roto i te wairua e haere mai ana ki ahau, nā te mea nō rātou hoki te kīngitanga o te rangi.

4 Hei āpiti anō, ka manaakitia te hunga katoa e tangi ana, nā te mea ka whakaāiotia rātou.

5 Ā, ka manaakitia te hunga māhaki, nā te mea nō rātou te whenua.

6 Ā, ka manaakitia te hunga katoa e hiakai ana, ā, e hiainu ana mō te tika, nā te mea ka whakakīngia rātou ki te Wairua Tapu.

7 Ā, ka manaakitia te hunga whakaaroha, nā te mea ka whiwhi rātou i te whakaaroha.

8 Ā, ka manaakitia te hunga katoa e ngākau mā ana, nā te mea ka kite rātou i te Atua.

9 Ā, ka manaakitia te hunga hohou rongo katoa, nā te mea ka karangatia rātou ko ngā tamariki a te Atua.

10 Ā, ka manaakitia te hunga katoa e whakatoia ana mō tōku ingoa, nā te mea nō rātou te kīngitanga o te rangi.

11 Ā, ka manaakitia koutou ina tāwaia koutou, ina whakatoia koutou, me te kōrero ake ki a koutou i ngā tūmomo kino teka, mōku te take;

12 Nā, ka whiwhi hoki koutou ki te hari me te koa nui, nā te mea ka nui tō utu i te rangi; nā, he pēnei anō tā rātou whakatoinga i ngā poropiti i mua i a koutou.

13 He pono, he pono, tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, ka hoatu au ki a koutou kia riro ai koutou hei tote mō te whenua; engari mēnā ka hemo te hā o te tote mā te aha e totengia ai te whenua? Ka riro te tote hei mea koretake, hei mea makaia noa iho ki waho, ā, hei mea takahia e ngā waewae o te tangata.

14 He pono, he pono, tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, ka hoatu au ki a koutou kia riro ai hei māramatanga mō tēnei iwi. Kāore e taea ana te huna i te pā e tū ana i runga i te puke.

15 Nana, ka whakakā te tangata i te kānara kātahi ka purua ki raro i tētahi ipu ine? Kāo, engari ka whakatūria ki runga i tētahi tūranga kānara, ā, ka tiaho atu ki ngā tāngata katoa i roto i te whare;

16 Nō reira kia tiaho tō koutou māramatanga i mua i tēnei iwi, kia kite ai rātou i ā koutou mahinga pai, ā, kia whakakorōria ai i tō koutou Matua i te rangi.

17 Kei whakaaro kua haere mai au ki te whakangaro i te ture, i ngā poropiti rānei. Kāore au i haere mai ki te whakangaro engari ki te whakatutuki;

18 Nā, he pono tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, kāore i pahemo atu tētahi tongi, tētahi tohu rānei i te ture, engari kua whakatutukihia ngā mea katoa i roto nei i ahau.

19 Ā nana, kua hoatu e au ki a koutou te ture me ngā whakahaunga a tōku Matua, kia whakapono ai koutou i ahau, ā, kia rīpenetā koutou i ō koutou hara, me te haere mai ki ahau i runga i te ngākau marū me te wairua iro. Nana, kei a koutou ngā whakahaunga i mua i a koutou, ā, kua whakatutukihia te ture.

20 Nō reira haere mai ki ahau, ā, kia whakaorangia ai koutou; nā, he pono tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, nā, ki te kore koutou e pupuri i aku whakahaunga, kua whakahaua nei koutou i tēnei wā, e kore rawa koutou e kuhu atu ki roto i te kīngitanga o te rangi.

21 Kua rongo koutou, nā, kua kōrerotia nei e te hunga onamata, ā, kua tuhia anō hoki i mua i tō koutou aroaro, kia kaua koutou e whakamate, ā, ka werewere iho te whakawākanga a te Atua ki runga i te tangata e whakamate ana;

22 Engari ko taku kupu tēnei ki a koutou, ka werewere iho tōna whakawākanga ki runga i te tangata e riri nei ki tana teina. Ā, ko te tangata e kī ake nei ki tana teina, Wairangi, ka werewere iho te rūnangatanga; ko te tangata e kī ai, He heahea koe, ka werewere iho te ahi o te ao rēwera.

23 Nō reira, ki te haere mai koutou ki ahau, ki te hiahia rānei kia haere mai ki ahau, ā, e mahara tonu ana kua hara tō teina ki a koe—

24 Haere i runga i tō huarahi ki tō teina, ā, me matua hohou i te rongo ki tō teina, kātahi ka haere mai ki ahau i runga i te hiahia katoa o te ngākau, ā, māku koe e whiwhi.

25 Kia hohoro tāu whakaae ki tō hoariri i a koe e haere tahi ana me ia i te huarahi, kei mau koe i a ia, ā, ka makaia atu koe ki roto i te whareherehere.

26 He pono, he pono, tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, e kore rawa koutou e puta mai i reira kia utua rā anō te henine whakamutunga. Ā, i a koe i roto i te whareherehere ka taea rānei e koe te henine kotahi noa iho te utu? He pono, he pono, tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, Kāo.

27 Nana, kua tuhia nei e rātou te hunga onamata, kia kaua koe e mahi pūremu;

28 Engari ko taku kupu tēnei ki a koutou, ko te tangata e titiro atu ana ki runga i tētahi wahine, he mate kanehe atu ki a ia, kua mahi pūremu atu ia i tōna ngākau.

29 Nana, kei te hoatu nei e au tētahi whakahaunga ki a koutou, kia kaua e tuku tētahi o ēnei mea kia kuhu ai ki roto i ō koutou ngākau;

30 Nā te mea he pai ake kia whakakahoretia atu e koutou ēnei mea, hei konei amohia ake e koutou ō koutou rīpeka, i te tuku kia makaia atu koutou ki roto i te ao rēwera.

31 Kua tuhia nei, ko te tangata e whakarere nei i tana hoawahine, tukuna ia kia hoatu ai e ia tētahi tuhinga whakarere.

32 He pono, he pono, tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, ko te tangata e whakarere i tana hoawahine, hāunga te take pūremu, e mea ana ia i te wahine kia pūremu; ā, ka pūremu te tangata e mārena ai ki a ia.

33 Hei āpiti anō kua tuhia nei, kaua koe e oati teka, engari me whakamahi āu oati ki te Ariki;

34 Engari he pono, he pono, tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, kaua rawa e oati; kaua rānei mā runga i te rangi, nā te mea koia te torona o te Atua;

35 Kaua rānei mā runga i te whenua, nā te mea koia tōna tūrangawaewae;

36 Kaua rānei koutou e oati mā runga i tō māhunga, nā te mea tē taea e koutou te mea kia mangu, kia mā rānei te makawe kotahi;

37 Engari tukuna tēnei hei kupu mā koutou Āe rā, āe rā; Kāo, kāo; nā te mea he kino ngā mea i tua atu i ēnei.

38 Ā nana, kua tuhia, he karu mō te karu, ā, he niho mō te niho;

39 Engari ko taku kupu tēnei ki a koutou, nā, kaua koutou e whakauaua atu i te kino, engari ko te tangata e papaki iho i tō pāpāringa matau, hurihia atu tētahi atu ki a ia anō hoki;

40 Mehemea ka hāmene tētahi tangata i a koe me te tango atu i tō koti, tukuna ia kia mau ki tō koti anō hoki;

41 Ā, ko te tangata e tono atu nei i a koe kia haere kotahi maero, haere tahi me ia mō ngā mea e rua.

42 Hoatu ki te tangata e tono ana i a koe, ā, kaua anō e tahuri atu i te tangata e hiahia ana ki te tono taonga tārewa i a koe.

43 Ā nana kua tuhia anō hoki, kia aroha atu koe ki tō kiritata, ā, kia mauāhara ki tōu hoariri;

44 Engari nana ko taku kupu tēnei ki a koutou, kia arohaina ō koutou hoariri, kia manaakitia te hunga e kangaia nei koutou, kia mahi pai ki te hunga e mauāhara nei ki a koutou, ā, kia inoi mō te hunga e whakamahia kinotia ana koutou, ā, e whakatoi ana i a koutou;

45 Kia riro koutou hei tamariki nā tō koutou Matua i te rangi; nā te mea ka mea ia i tana rā kia whiti iho ai ki runga i te hunga kino me te hunga pai.

46 Nō reira ko aua mea nō onamata, i raro iho nei i te ture, kua whakatutukihia ērā mea katoa i roto i ahau.

47 Kua whakakorea atu ngā mea tawhito, ā, kua meinga houhia ngā mea katoa.

48 Nō reira e hiahia ana ahau kia tika rawa atu koutou pērā i ahau, pērā rānei i tō koutou Matua kei roto nei i te rangi e tika rawa atu ana.

3-ne 21:
[center][font_size=26]Upoko 21[/font_size][/center]

[i]Ka whakahuihui a Iharaira ina puta mai te Pukapuka a Moromona—Ka whakapūmauhia ngā Tauiwi hei iwi herekore i Amerika—Ka whakaorangia rātou mehemea ka whakapono, ā, ka ngohengohe rātou; ki te kore, ka hātepea atu rātou, ā, ka whakangaromia—Ka hanga a Iharaira i te Hiruharama Hou, ā, ka hoki atu ngā hapū ngaro. Takiwā T.A. 34.[/i]

1 Ā, he pono tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, ka hoatu e au he tohu ki a koutou, kia mōhio ai koutou hei āhea te wā e tū ai ēnei mea—kia kohikohia mai e au, mai i tā rātou mararatanga roa, tōku iwi, E te whare o Iharaira, me te whakapūmau anō i tōku Hīona ki waenganui i a rātou.

2 Ā nana, anei te mea e hoatu nei e au ki a koutou hei tohu—nā te mea he pono tāku ki a koutou, nā, ina whakamōhiotia atu ēnei mea e whakapuaki atu nei au ki a koutou, ā, mōku ake anō ngā mea e whakapuaki atu nei au ki a koutou, me te mana o te Wairua Tapu e hoatu ai ki a koutou e te Matua, ka whakamōhiotia atu anō ki ngā Tauiwi e mōhio ai rātou e pā ana ki tēnei iwi, ko rātou nei he mōrehu nō te whare o Hākopa, ā, e pā ana anō hoki ki tēnei tōku iwi e whakamararatia atu ai e rātou;

3 He pono, he pono, tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, ina whakamōhiotia atu ēnei mea ki a rātou e te Matua, ā, mā te Matua ki a rātou, mā rātou ki a koutou;

4 Nā, he mātauranga nui nō te Matua kia whakapūmauhia rātou i tēnei whenua, ā, kia whakaritea hei iwi herekore i runga i te mana o te Matua, kia puta mai ai ēnei mea i a rātou ki ngā mōrehu o ōu uri, kia whakatutuki pai i te kawenata a te Matua nāna nei i kawenata ki tana iwi, E te whare o Iharaira;

5 Nō reira, ina puta mai ēnei mahi me ngā mahi e tau ai ki runga i a koutou a muri ake nei i ngā Tauiwi, ki ō koutou uri e memeha atu ai i te whakapono kore he mea nā tō rātou kino;

6 Nā, he tikanga hoki tēnei ki tā te Matua kia puta mai ai ēnei mea i ngā Tauiwi, kia whakakitea atu e ia tōna kaha ki ngā Tauiwi mō tēnei take, arā, ki te kore ngā Tauiwi e whakapakeke i ō rātou ngākau, kia taea ai e rātou te rīpenetā me te haere mai ki ahau, ā, kia rumakina i runga i tōku ingoa me te mōhio ki ngā tikanga tūturu o taku akoranga, kia tatauria ai rātou i waenganui i tōku iwi, E te whare o Iharaira;

7 Ā, ina pahawa ake ēnei mea e tīmata ai ōu uri ki te mōhio ki ēnei mea—ka tū ai hei tohu ki a rātou, kia mōhio ai rātou kua tīmata kē te mahi a te Matua ki te whakatutuki i te kawenata i kawenata ai ia ki te iwi ko rātou nei te whare o Iharaira.

8 Ā, ina tae mai taua rā, ka pahawa ake, nā, ka kopi ngā kīngi i ō rātou māngai; nā te mea ka kite rātou i ērā mea kīhai noa i kōrerotia ki a rātou; ā, ka whakaarohia e rātou ērā mea kīhai noa i rangona.

9 Nā, hei taua rā, ka mahi te Matua i tētahi mahi mōku te take, he mahi nui whakamīharo ki waenganui i a rātou; ā, ki waenganui i te hunga e kore nei e whakapono, ahakoa ka whakapuakina e tētahi tangata ki a rātou.

10 Engari nana, kei tōku ringa te oranga o taku pononga; nō reira e kore nei rātou e whakamamae i a ia, ahakoa ka hakokengia ia e rātou. Heoi māku ia e mahū, nā te mea ka whakakite atu au ki a rātou he nui ake tōku mātauranga i tō te rēwera tinihanga.

11 Nō reira ka pahawa ake, nā, ko ngā tāngata e kore nei e whakapono ki aku kupu, ko ahau nei a Ihu Karaiti, ko tērā e meinga ai e te Matua kia whakaputaina mai ai ki ngā Tauiwi, ā, ka hoatu mana ki a ia kia whakaputaina mai ai ki ngā Tauiwi, (ka meatia pērā i tā Mohi i kī ai) ka hātepea atu rātou i tōku iwi, nō te kawenata rātou.

12 Ā, ka noho i waenganui tōku iwi ko rātou nei he mōrehu o Hākopa ki waenganui i ngā Tauiwi, āe rā, kei waenganui i a rātou anō nei he raiona i waenganui i ngā kararehe o te ngahere, anō nei he kūao raiona i waenganui i ngā kāhui hipi, koia, ki te haere ia ki roto rā, ka takahia, ā, ka haehaea, ā, kāore e taea e tētahi te whakaora.

13 Ka hikina ake tō rātou ringa ki runga i ō rātou hoariri, ā, ka hātepea atu ō rātou hoariri katoa.

14 Āe rā, auē te mate mō ngā Tauiwi ki te kore rātou e rīpenetā; nā te mea ka pahawa ake i taua rā, e ai tā te Matua, ka hātepea atu e au ōu hōiho i tō aroaro, ā, māku ōu hāriata e whakangaro;

15 Ā, ka hātepea atu e au ngā pā o tōu whenua, ā, ka whiua iho ōu pākaha katoa;

16 Ā, ka hātepea atu e au ngā mākutu i roto i tōu whenua, ā, kua kore anō ō tohunga matakite;

17 Ka hātepea atu anō e au ō whakapakoko, me ō pou whakaahua i tōu aroaro, ā, e kore tonu atu koe e koropiko i ngā mahinga o ōu ringaringa;

18 Ā, ka hutia ake e au ō uru rākau i tōu aroaro; ka whakangaromia anōtia e au ō pā.

19 Ā, ka pahawa ake, nā, ka whakakorengia atu āu rūkahu, me āu tinihanga, me āu pūhaehae, me āu tautohetohenga, me āu mahi tohunga teka, me āu mahi pūremu,

20 Nā te mea ka pahawa ake, e ai tā te Matua, ko ngā tāngata e kore nei e rīpenetā me te haere mai ki taku Tama Aroha, ko rātou nei ngā mea e hātepea atu ai e au i tōku iwi, E te whare o Iharaira;

21 Ā, māku e rapu utu me te riri ki runga i a rātou, ka rite anō ki te mea i runga i ngā tangata mātauranga kore, he mea kīhai i rangona noatia e rātou i mua.

22 Engari ki te rīpenetā rātou me te whakarongo ki aku kupu, ā, ka kore hoki e whakapakeke i ō rātou ngākau, ka whakapūmau au i tōku hāhi ki waenganui i a rātou, ā, ka uru mai rātou ki te kawenata, ā, ka tatauria ki waenganui i tēnei ngā mōrehu o Hākopa, kua hoatu e au ki a rātou tēnei whenua hei mea tuku iho mō rātou;

23 Ā, ka āwhina rātou i tōku iwi, ngā mōrehu o Hākopa, ā, i te hunga katoa anō hoki nō te whare o Iharaira e haere mai ai, kia hangaia ake he pā, e karangatia nei ko te Hiruharama Hou.

24 Kātahi rātou ka āwhina i tōku iwi kia whakahuihui mai anō i a rātou, ko rātou nei ngā mea kua whakamararatia atu i runga i te mata katoa o te whenua, ki roto ki te Hiruharama Hou.

25 Kātahi ka heke iho te mana o te rangi ki runga i a rātou; ā, ko au anō hoki kei tō rātou aroaro.

26 Kātahi ka tīmata te mahi a te Matua i taua rā, ina kauhautia atu tēnei rongopai ki waenganui i ngā mōrehu o tēnei iwi. He pono tāku e mea atu nei ki a koutou, hei taua rā tīmata ai te mahi a te Matua ki waenganui i te hunga o tōku iwi katoa kua whakamararatia atu nei, āe rā, ki ngā hapū anō kua ngaro atu nei, kua ārahina atu nei e te Matua ki waho atu i Hiruharama.

27 Āe rā, ka tīmata te mahi ki waenganui i te hunga o tōku iwi katoa kua whakamararatia atu nei, mā te Matua te huarahi e whakarite mā konā haere mai ai rātou ki ahau, kia karanga ake rātou ki te Matua i runga i tōku ingoa.

28 Āe rā, kātahi ka tīmata te mahi a te Matua i roto i ngā iwi katoa e whakarite ana i te huarahi mā konā whakahuihui mai anō tōna iwi ki tō rātou whenua tuku iho.

29 Ā, ka haere atu rātou i ngā whenua katoa; ā, kua kore rātou e haere kaikā atu, kāore rānei e tūāoma, nā te mea ka haere ahau i mua i a rātou, e ai tā te Matua, ā, māku anō hei hiku mō rātou.
